## Guardrails
- Never move capital onto Kalshi in excess of `kalshi_active` allocation — keep reserve liquid
- Loss stoppage policies must be reviewed and re-confirmed with Risk Quant monthly
- All infrastructure cost changes (upgrades/downgrades) require Treasury sign-off
- Track gross AND net P&L — a "profitable" bot that loses to fees and costs is not profitable
- Capital scaling decisions require PM + Treasury + Risk Quant approval — no unilateral increases
